text: The 2017 Liga 3 Special Region of Yogyakarta season is the third edition of Liga 3 Special Region of Yogyakarta is a qualifying round of the 2017 Liga 3. Gama F.C. are the defending champions. The competition scheduled starts on April 2017. ==Teams== This season there are 10 club will participate the league. {| class="wikitable" |- !
